org.melior.logging.appender

Class Appender

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.melior.logging.appender.Appender
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsoleAppender, FileAppender

    public abstract class Appender
extends Object
    Base class for internal log appenders that write trace logs and/or transaction logs. Provides access to the logging stream and to the logger configuration to allow an appender to configure itself.
    Since:
    2.1
    Author:
    Melior
    See Also:
    Stream, Configuration
